Hey

HTMLBars (sort of the Handlebars dialect Ember.js uses) has so called block components invoked like this:

``` handlebars
{{#each whateverList as |key value|}}
  {{key}}: {{value}}
{{/each}}
```

in vscode `whateverList as |key value|` is completely light blue, i'd expect the at least the `as` and the pipes to have a slightly different color, maybe the darker blue of the each.

BR
Domme

Hey,

methods in POJOs don't autocomplete like here:

``` javascript
var foo = {
    bar() {
    }

    baz() {
        this.bar<ctrl+space>
    }
}
```

although it works just fine for ES6 classes:

``` javascript
class Foo  {
    bar() {
    }

    baz() {
        this.bar<ctrl+space>
    }
}
```

BR
Dominik
